name: Future Foundry
description:
Year 2492: Mike, a 39 years
old man, is a worker at the
Future Foundry, the biggest
foundry in the industrial area
of Night Valley. He makes sure
no toxic waste is generated
through the material quality
control. He lives in a small
apartment nearby, paid by the
corporation, with his wife, his
daughter and their cat, Lilo.
